window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Prepare to embark on a truly remarkable journey as you witness the profound and transformative power of love, defying all expectations, as two wounded souls come together to heal, find solace, and form an unbreakable connection. Enter the world of Beth, a successful businesswoman who owns a successful bakery. The stress in her personal life as she navigates a challenging divorce and the pain of unmet expectations is hidden by her professional success. But when Ryan, a charming ex-marine, enters her bakery, fate has a surprise in store. They are shocked when a deep connection is created and sparks fly. </p> <p>Ryan is burdened by his military experience and his family's strained connection. In Beth's company, he finds comfort and the possibility of a new beginning. They work through the difficulties of their issues as a team, finding comfort, healing, and love in one other's embrace. Watch as they overcome personal and professional obstacles while navigating the delicate dance of love. </p> <p>Learn how love may heal, transform, and spark your soul when it comes to you unexpectedly in <i>Kneading Hearts: A Sweet Story of Rekindled Dreams, Second Chances, and New Beginnings</i>.</p>"; 
